  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ZCBC Capacity Development Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of this project is to strengthen the institutional capacity of the Zimbabwe Catholic Bishops&#x2019; Conference (ZCBC) and Caritas Zimbabwe National Office, in accordance with the priorities established by the 2013-7 strategic plan. 

This will be achieved through enabling the Secretary General and his management team to control systems, processes and structures through:
- improving financial management and accountability systems, with the creation of a finance department, recruitment of a finance manager and a review of financial control systems;
- enhancing managerial skills and performance standards, with the recruitment of a personnel manager; revision of the HR manual and implementation of its statutes; drafting/revision of job descriptions and the adoption of a code of ethics.</narrative>
  </description>
